detail_desc: Hat in a soft cable knit with a faux fur pompom on top and earflaps with ties. Fleece lining.
Wide trousers in a soft weave with a high waist, detachable tie belt, concealed zip fly with a hook-and-eye fastening and side pockets.
Trousers in woven fabric. High waist with pleats and a detachable tie belt, a concealed hook-and-eye fastener and a zip fly. Side pockets and tapered legs with creases.

Sporty jacket in sturdy jersey with a zip down the front and a mesh-lined hood with an elastic drawstring. Chest pocket with a concealed zip, side pockets, ribbed cuffs and narrow elastication at the hem.
Rib-knit hat in a soft cotton blend with a roll-edge hem.
5-pocket jeans in washed denim with a regular waist, button fly and straight-cut legs that taper gently to the hem.
Soft cap in UV-protective fabric with a peak at the front and flap at the back to protect both the face and back of the neck. UPF 50.
Jersey T-shirt.

Calf-length dress in an airy weave with an opening and button at the back of the neck. Voluminous, 3/4-length puff sleeves with narrow, covered elastication at the cuffs, and a gathered seam at the waist.
Short, V-neck dress in jersey with gathers at the shoulders and short, wide sleeves. Tapered waist with gathered seams for a gently draped effect. Lined.
Slim-fit trousers in washed, superstretch twill with hard-worn details, front and back pockets and narrow, raw-edge, frayed hems.
KIDS EXCLUSIVE. Trousers in soft, organic slub cotton jersey with an elasticated waist, fly with decorative buttons, side pockets and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.
Long-sleeved top in soft jersey with flounce-trimmed cut-out sections at the shoulders.
Brazilian briefs in cotton jersey with a high waist, lined gusset, high-cut legs and half-string back.
Jumper in a soft, loose knit with a V-neck, long raglan sleeves and roll edges at the cuffs and hem. Longer at the back.
Imitation leather trainers with a hook and loop fastening at the front and a soft, padded top edge. Mesh linings and insoles.
Sports vest top in a double layer of soft, fast-drying functional fabric with a racer back.
5-pocket jeans in washed stretch denim with a regular waist, button fly and slim legs.
Long-sleeved top in a rib knit. Low-cut neckline with a twisted detail at the back.

Shirt in a woven cotton blend with a turn-down collar, French front, long sleeves with adjustable buttoning at the cuffs and a rounded hem. Slim fit with narrow shoulders and a tapered waist for a fitted silhouette.
Trousers in woven fabric with a high waist, buttons and pleats at the front, side pockets, fake welt pockets at the back, a slightly lower crotch and straight legs.
Straight-cut coat with a soft, brushed finish, notch lapels, concealed press-studs down the front and welt front pockets. Unlined.
Loose-fitting sports vest top in fast-drying jersey with a racer back.
Scarf in an airy weave with fringes along the sides.
Straight-cut T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a motif on the front and narrow trim around the neckline.

High-waisted jeans in stretch denim with a zip fly and extended waistband with a press-stud fastening. Zipped side pocket, vertical seams front and back and straight legs with flared, asymmetric hems.
Gently flared skirt in a soft, fine knit with covered elastication at the waist.
Vest tops in soft jersey with narrow shoulder straps, a small scalloped trim at the top and a decorative bow at the front.
5-pocket slim-fit jeans in washed, superstretch denim for maximum mobility with an adjustable, elasticated waist, zip fly and button, and narrow hems.

Relaxed-fit joggers in stretch cotton twill with a lightly brushed finish. Elasticated drawstring waist, a fake fly, side pockets and jetted back pockets. Slightly lower crotch and tapered legs with ribbing at the hems.
Baby Exclusive. Shorts in soft, ribbed organic cotton jersey with covered elastication at the waist and overlocked hems.
Gently fitted jacket in a textured weave with a concealed hook-and-eye fastening at the front, welt front pockets and sleeves with gathered seams. Lined.

Fully lined sports bra in extra-sturdy, fast-drying functional fabric that shapes and sculpts the bust. Removable inserts, a racer back and a wide, double-layered hem with a scalloped edge. Extra firm support.
Ankle-length trousers in a textured weave with a regular elasticated, drawstring waist, pockets in the side seams and straight, wide legs.
T-shirt in cotton jersey.
Large scarf in soft, gently draping satin with an all-over print.
Lace bra top with a deep V-neck front and back, decorative buttons at the front and short cap sleeves. No fasteners.
Knee-length dress in a viscose weave with embroidery on the front, a deep V-neck and long sleeves with narrow elastication at the cuffs. Elasticated seam at the waist. Unlined.
Top in soft fabric with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Treggings in sturdy jersey with an elasticated waist.
Metal earrings with narrow hoops and a round pendant with a plastic stone at the bottom. Length approx. 4 cm.
5-pocket jeans in washed stretch denim with a regular waist, zip fly and button at the waist, and skinny legs.
Fully lined bikini bottoms with a mid waist and medium coverage at the back.
Jumper in soft, fine knit lambswool with a round, ribbed neckline and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Blouse in woven fabric with a collar, buttons down the front, gathers at the shoulders, long sleeves with buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.
Short-sleeved nursing tops in soft jersey made from a cotton blend. Double-layered front with a practical inner top for easier nursing access. The cotton content of the tops is organic.
Jumper in a soft viscose-blend knit with a V-neck and inset lace section at the back. Long sleeves with a wide lace edge at the end.
Long-sleeved top in soft cotton jersey with press-studs on one shoulder.
Long-sleeved jumper in soft, fine-knit cotton with a reversible sequin motif on the front and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Top in softly draping, ribbed jersey with a sheen. Narrow shoulder straps, a V-neck at the front and a lace trim at the top.

Push-up bra in lace and mesh with decorative, crossover straps at the front and underwired, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Adjustable shoulder straps and a hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Ballet pumps in imitation leather with a bow at the front, a grosgrain trim around the top and an elastic strap over the foot. Satin linings and insoles and fluted soles.
Top in lightweight cotton sweatshirt fabric in a relaxed fit with long raglan sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Metal and plastic earrings in various designs. Length from 4.5 cm to 8 cm.
Trousers in soft sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, zipped side pockets, a decorative back pocket and ribbed hems. Soft brushed inside.
Short dress in a crêpe weave with a V-neck and wrapover front with concealed press-studs. Short sleeves and a seam at the waist with a sewn-in tie belt.
Sun hat in braided paper straw with a band in a crêpe weave. Width of brim approx. 12 cm.
Cardigan in soft, fine-knit cotton with a V-neck, buttons down the front and elbow patches in a contrasting colour.
5-pocket low-rise jeans in washed denim with hard-worn details, a button fly and slightly wider, tapered legs.
Sleeveless top in soft jersey with a flounce at the top.
Longer hooded top in soft fleece with long raglan sleeves, a kangaroo pocket and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft and fluffy inside.

KIDS EXCLUSIVE. Trousers in double-weave, crinkled organic cotton with an adjustable, elasticated waist and zip fly with a button. Side pockets, a back pocket and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems. Detachable elastic braces with imitation leather details.

Padded parka in woven fabric with a soft, lightly brushed finish. Stand-up collar, zip and wind flap with hook and loop fasteners down the front, flap front pockets with press-studs and ribbing at the cuffs.
Lined, non-wired bikini top with wide shoulder straps and padded cups with removable inserts that shape the bust and provide good support. Knot detail at the front and a metal fastener at the back.
Fabric-covered hair elastics with a bow.
Suede sandals with covered heels and a braided jute trim around the soles. Elastic strap over the foot, open toes and leather insoles. Platform front 3 cm, heel 9.5 cm.
Hair elastics without metal clips.
Scarf in soft woven fabric with a brushed finish. Fringes on the short sides. Size 35x180 cm.
Thong briefs in lace and mesh with a low waist, lined gusset, wide sides and string back.
Jumper in soft, jacquard-knit cotton with long sleeves, buttons on one shoulder and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Short skirt in stretch twill made from a cotton blend with fake pockets and buttons down the front.
Sleeveless top in printed cotton jersey with a frill around the armholes.
Knee-length shorts in lightweight sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend with a print motif, ribbed elasticated drawstring waist and side pockets.
Three-strand anklet of thin metal chains in various designs, one with a coin-shaped pendant. Adjustable length, 20-26 cm.
V-neck top in cool, softly draping silk with adjustable spaghetti shoulder straps.
Short, fitted top in ribbed jersey with long sleeves and a visible seam down the front. Slightly shorter front with a twisted detail at the hem.
Fitted, long-sleeved dress in pattern-weave jersey with a round neckline and an opening with a button at the back of the neck. Lined.
Satin tie. Width 6.5 cm. The polyester content of the tie is partly recycled.
Leggings in heavy, organic cotton jersey with a soft brushed inside. Skinny fit with an easy pull-on, elasticated waist.
